      "writtenOn": "2020-08-21T05:33:56Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "How about using filepath.Dir(f) as baseDir? Then we need less magic strings (e.g. \"/etc/ssh/ssh_config\"), and it\u0027ll be easier to write unit tests because we can avoid reading /etc/ssh or ~/.ssh in unit tests.",
