      },
      "lineNbr": 247,
      "author": {
        "id": 1431492
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-08-22T00:23:13Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t really want to call it *Glob* because glob does not take care of tilde and does not use base directory. How about \"expandFilePath\" which I think it is an appropriate name? Let\u0027s discuss it. Thanks.",
      "parentUuid": "84cf01de_3e64302e",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 247,
        "startChar": 5,
        "endLine": 247,
        "endChar": 23
      },
      "revId": "25a7b89ba13db41735f87cded32b14c61c89cc97",
