        "id": 1431492
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-08-22T00:23:13Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Thanks for the link. I took a quick look at the link and found that my unit did not follow the standard. I have broken it down. Also, my unit test was testing ResloveHostWithFromFiles instead of ResolveHost which was called by run.go. Therefore, I combined these two functions into one. Hope it is ok.",
      "parentUuid": "6aa5850d_a1bcc62c",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 83,
        "startChar": 5,
        "endLine": 83,
        "endChar": 29
      },
      "revId": "25a7b89ba13db41735f87cded32b14c61c89cc97",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "key": {
