      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-08-21T05:33:56Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t recommend sharing the same config files for many (sub-)test cases. While it looks simple and short initially, this approach tends to be difficult to add more test cases later.",
